# Version 2: NGINX + PM2 Optimized Deployment

> **Production-ready Node.js deployment demonstrating 60-70% performance improvement over baseline**

This deployment package represents **Version 2** of the Urine Disease Detection System, optimized with NGINX reverse proxy, PM2 cluster mode, and production-grade Node.js optimizations. It demonstrates best practices for high-performance microservices deployment suitable for thesis research validation.

