Based on optimizations above:

| Metric | Version 1 | Version 2 | Improvement |
|--------|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| p95 Latency (100 VUs) | 8000ms | 2500ms | **69% faster** |
| Throughput (100 VUs) | 15 req/s | 40 req/s | **167% higher** |
| Error Rate (100 VUs) | 50% | 5% | **90% reduction** |
| Memory Usage | 800MB | 750MB | **6% lower** |

